graphql.query:
query ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	oAuthGetAccessTokens (query: $query)
	{
		id
		accountId
		token
		name
		isRevoked
		expiresAt
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

query ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	oAuthFindAccessToken (query: $query)
	{
		id
		accountId
		token
		name
		isRevoked
		expiresAt
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

query ($id:ID)
{
	oAuthFindAccessTokenById (id:$id)
	{
		id
		accountId
		token
		name
